title: Miss Ye in Wonderland
overview: Office worker Ye Wan Ge got into a car accident and woke up to find that she had turned into a character. Ye Wang Ge thinks she can return to reality if she puts together the male lead Feng Mu Chen and the virtuous female lead Lu Wang Qing. Failing again and again, Ye Wan Ge realizes that she can only truly leave after completing life's tasks in history.Adaptation of the web novel "Qian Jin Tai Xiao Zhang" by Qian Chen Yuan Ge (前尘远歌).
